The popular Nigerian singer, songwriter, and multiple brand ambassador, Portable Omolalami, popularly known as ‘Werey Olorin, Idamu Adugbo, and Zazoo’ has revealed that he has bagged another multi-million naira endorsement with a big company in Nigeria. Many people have congratulated him in the comments section on Instagram.
Recently, Portable signed a 50 million naira endorsement with a popular Nigerian businessman, Obinna Iyiegbu, popularly known as Obi Cubana. There’s no doubt, Portable is currently one of the millionaire upcoming singers in Nigeria.
While sharing the good news on his official Instagram Instagram, he wrote:
“It has been God always. Another Endorsement deal. Another company (Name withheld) don show love oooo Bizza Bizza”
The popular Nigerian billionaire, Obi Cubana reacted with fire and love emojis.
The popular Nigerian singer, Samklef also reacted with emojis.
Read how people congratulated him in the comments section on Instagram



